<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/cabinet-office-board> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Cabinet Office board provides the collective strategic and operational leadership of the Department, bringing together Cabinet Office Ministers, senior members of the Department’s executive leadership team with senior Non-Executives from outside government. Cabinet Office Board is part of the Cabinet Office ."@en .
